quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  100,10,"Waxa ku jirana laabaha la caddeeyo."
  100,11,"Hubaal Rabbigood maalintaas waa u Xog-Ogaal (arrimahooda oo dhan)."
  101,7,"Wuxuu ku noolaan nolol barwaaqo iyo farxad leh oo raalli lagu yahay (Janno)."
  101,8,"Qofkase uu miisaankiisa (camallada wanaagsan) fudeyd yahay."
  101,9,"Hoygiisu waa Haawiya."
  102,4,"Misna, mayee! Waad ogaan doontaan."
  102,5,"Mayee! haddaad og tihiin ogaansho dhab ah."
  102,6,"Waxaad hubaal arki Naarta ololka badan."
  103,1,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay waqtiga."
  103,2,"Hubaal Aadmigu wuxuu ku sugan yahay khasaaro dhan."
  103,3,"Kuwa (Xaqa) rumeeyey mooyee oo samaha fala, ee isu dardaraama Xaqa (iyo caddaalad falka), isuna dardaarama sabarka (iyo sugnaanta)."